  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this prospective follow-up study is to investigate 5-year clinical outcome in
      patients with ST-elevation myocardial infarction undergoing remote ischemic conditioning
      before primary percutaneous coronary intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
