  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Chest pain before admission to hospital within 12 h of onset, ST-segment elevation of
             &gt; 0,1 mV in 2 or more contiguous leads, 18 years or older.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  left bundle branch block, previous myocardial infarction, fibrinolytic treatment in
             the previous 30 days, previous coronary bypass surgery, left main stem stenosis
             requiring coronary bypass surgery, severe heart failure requiring mechanical
             ventilation or use of an intra-aortic balloon pump.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
